  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/System\/Errno\/alreadyInProcess\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T22:03:33Z\n---\n\n# alreadyInProcess\n\n**Type Property**\n\nOperation already in progress.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nstatic var alreadyInProcess: Errno { get }\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nYou attempted an operation on a nonblocking object that already had an operation in progress.\n\nThe corresponding C error is `EALREADY`.\n\n## System Call Errors\n\n- **badAddress**: Bad address.\n- **interrupted**: Interrupted function call.\n- **invalidArgument**: Invalid argument.\n- **noFunction**: Function not implemented.\n- **nowInProgress**: Operation now in progress.\n- **resourceBusy**: Resource busy.\n- **resourceTemporarilyUnavailable**: Resource temporarily unavailable.\n\n",
